{"title":"火炬","authors":["关振东"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":11,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"火炬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"关振东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深夜，听完村史的山民们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向四面八方归去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"背上背着孩子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手中擎着火篱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一支支火炬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪耀在夜空里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旗一样红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花一般美。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火炬在手上燃烧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热血在胸中冲激，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村史展览会上的情景，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唤起了幕幕辛酸的回忆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宽底的方斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盛着山民几代的深仇？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无情的大秤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连穷人的骨髓也钩走！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灯光下，陈封的帐簿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一行就是一条性命；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而带刺的“马棒”呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明明还散发着血腥！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死难弟兄的尸骨未寒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心上的伤痕刚刚熨平。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说往事已成烟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"豺狼已经改性。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看，落水狗摇着柔顺的尾巴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"獠牙却露出噬人的狰狞；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你听，那阿谀的谄笑里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是夹着阴险的嗥声？！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深夜，听完村史的山民们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心潮伏了又起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男人们都把衣襟敞开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妇女们默默不语。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在深蓝色的夜空里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火炬的队伍在行进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一点，一颗心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燃烧着阶级的热情！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去远了，像颗颗星星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪烁着，比星星更光明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它将永远在人们的心上燃烧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照耀着前进的途程！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}